{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ABOUT THIS GAME </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Murmurs of Fear</strong> is an episodic psychological horror game where each episode tells a short story from the perspective of those who managed to retain their sanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/\u0421\u044e\u0436\u0435\u0442_en.png?t=1735738412\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the first episode, <strong>Murmurs of Fear - A Whisper of Loneliness</strong>, you play as Alexey, a 22-year-old young man who recently qualified as an electrician and was sent to assist a group of geologists tasked with opening old, preserved mines on an island with a lighthouse. The island had long shown no signs of life, and upon arriving, you discover that the geologists are missing. Left alone on the eerie island, you must uncover mysteries, solve puzzles, and survive the lurking horrors. Can you survive the night and uncover the truth?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/\u041e\u0441\u043e\u0431\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u0438_en.png?t=1735738412\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key features of the first episode:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lovecraftian aesthetics and the atmosphere of old detective stories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Realistic environments with a VHS game vibe.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Non-linear storytelling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Exploring mysteries in foggy settings.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/\u041c\u0435\u0445\u0430\u043d\u0438\u043a\u0438_en.png?t=1735738412\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In this part of the game:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Uncover the island\u2019s secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with the environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decide which ending you\u2019ll achieve.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/extras/\u041a\u0432\u0435\u0441\u0442\u044b_en.png?t=1735738412\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You will need to:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Investigate the disappearance of the geologists.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Repair equipment on the island.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gather clues and solve puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use a trolley to navigate the island. </p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735738412","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/page.bg.jpg?t=1735738412","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735738412","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129900/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735738412","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Captions available","id":13},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"HDR available","id":61}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ABOUT THIS GAME </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Murmurs of Fear</strong> is an episodic psychological horror game where each episode tells a short story from the perspective of those who managed to retain their sanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://sha